data.description: Welcome to your new home! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is situated on a spacious corner lot, offering both privacy and curb appeal.  The well-manicured front yard invites you into the property, where you'll find a fenced-in back yard that provides a secure space for your family and pets.  And that's not all - there's even an above-ground swimming pool, perfect for enjoying hot summer days and entertaining guests.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the open floor plan, creating a sense of warmth and togetherness.  The living area seamlessly connects to the kitchen, allowing for easy interaction with family and friends.  The kitchen boasts elegant granite counters, providing ample space for meal preparation and hosting gatherings.  The modern design  and high-quality materials make this kitchen a true centerpiece of the home.   One of the standout features of this house is the large laundry room.  With plenty of storage and counter spaces, this room ensures that laundry tasks are not only 'convenient but also organized.   You'll appreciate the efficiency and functionality it offers.   The Master Bedroom is a tranquil retreat, complete with a double vanity in the en-suite bathroom.  This feature provides both convenience and luxury, allowing you and your partner to have your own space while getting ready for the day.  The additional three bedrooms offer flexibility for a growing family, home office, or guest rooms.  Overall this move-in ready house checks all the boxes for a comfortable and stylish living experience.  From the corner lot and fenced-in back yard to the above-ground pool and open floor plan, it's the perfect place to call home!
